## ğŸ“ Release Notes

### v1.1.0 (Latest) - Advanced Fake Detection & Red-Green BDD
- âœ… **LLM-Powered Fake Detection**: Claude analyzes step files to catch sophisticated fakes
- âœ… **Dual-Phase Validation**: Combines regex patterns + LLM analysis for comprehensive detection
- âœ… **Red-Green BDD Enforcement**: Proper TDD workflow requiring tests to fail first
- âœ… **Two-Phase Claude Workflow**: Phase 1: Analyze fakes, Phase 2: Implement real code
- âœ… **Cross-Validation System**: Validates WarpCode parsing against actual behave execution
- âœ… **Enhanced Behavioral Testing**: File dependency tests, scenario isolation, truth verification
- âœ… **Comprehensive Fake Reports**: Auto-generates `fakesteps.md` documentation

### v1.0.9 - Comprehensive Monitoring & Conversation Continuity
- âœ… **Conversation Continuity**: Claude maintains context with `-c` flag support
- âœ… **Real-time OTEL Monitoring**: Live OpenTelemetry event parsing and display  
- âœ… **Enhanced Reality Validation**: Behavioral testing and fake pattern learning
- âœ… **Smart Environment Setup**: Prevents unnecessary re-initialization
- âœ… **Comprehensive Debug Output**: Full Claude activity visibility with timestamps
- âœ… **Validation Feedback Loop**: Failed validations inform subsequent prompts

### v1.0.8 - Reality Validation Foundation
- âœ… **Reality Validator**: Comprehensive fake implementation detection
- âœ… **Enhanced Claude Prompts**: Strict anti-mock enforcement with time limits
- âœ… **Improved Monitoring**: Initial OpenTelemetry integration

### v1.0.7 - Enhanced Dashboard & Monitoring
- âœ… **Activity Dashboard**: Real-time UI progress tracking
- âœ… **Scoreboard Management**: JSON-based status persistence
- âœ… **Claude Interface**: Automated execution with log monitoring

### v1.0.6 - Core BDD Integration
- âœ… **BDD Runner**: Behave integration with result parsing
